OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FExtensive
OL,6,Flow cloud with drizzle will affect
OL,7,Fsouthern and western areas overnight.
OL,8,FMeanwhile, heavier rain spreads in
OL,9,Ffrom the southwest across Northern
OL,10,FIreland and into Scotland and northern
OL,11,FEngland. Clear intervals to northeast
OL,12,Fof hills. Warm and muggy further south.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FOutbreaks of locally heavy
OL,15,Frain gradually easing in the north on
OL,16,FThursday. Hill and coastal fog with
OL,17,Fdrizzle affecting southern and western
OL,18,Fareas elsewhere. Meanwhile, hot
OL,19,Fsunshine in the southeast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
